[30;1m21 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m22 | [0m[35mBRLE is an optimized form for when the stored values can only be `0` or `1`.[0m
[30;1m23 | [0m[35mThis means we only need to save the counts, and assume the values alternate[0m
[30;1m24 | [0m[35m(starting at `0`).[0m
